Company Description: Founded IN 1962, Sedano's Supermarkets Is A Chain Of More Than 30 Grocery Stores IN Florida. The Company Is One Of The Largest Members Of The Associated Grocer's Of Florida. Its Stores Operate Cafeterias And Bakery, Dairy, Produce, Meat, Deli, Fishery And Hot Food Departments. IN Addition, Sedano's Supermarkets Offers A Variety Of Online Recipes For Its Customers.
